                <h1>Lyft</h1>
                <h2>2023 • Tap to Add Credit Card</h2>
                <q>I tried Lyft's credit card scanner and it messed up the number so I had to type it in myself which is really annoying.</q>
                <p>Adding a credit card during Lyft signup while trying to schedule a ride is a high friction event, so we leveraged NFC technology to allow riders to tap smart cards on their phone to automatically fill credit card fields.</p>
                <p>Rider maintained preference for manual entry, but the tap to add option won out over the photo capture option by almost 2 to 1.</p>
            </div>
