                <h2>2022 • Notification Center</h2>
                <q>...email is the only reference documentation I get from Affirm, I have nowhere else to put all your notifications together...</q>
                <p>Introduced a notifications feed in the Affirm app to help customers improve access to messaging from Affirm and take action on critical alerts.</p>
                <p>Launch saw an overall 1% attributed increase in loan repayment rates amongst customers exposed to Phase 1 of this feature.</p>
                <p><a href="https://www.figma.com/file/Z6ynTFkkTT6ulusqfagyLr/portfolio?type=design&node-id=920%3A2152&mode=design&t=QaAWrVt3ZoaAdzhD-1" class="button">Read case study</a></p>
