                <h1>Affirm</h1>
                <h2>2021 • Loan Repayment Redesign</h2>
                <q>I get lost trying to find how to make a payment and easily lose track of what payment is due when.</q>
                <p>Updated the Affirm loan repayment experience to better scale for new functionality and encourage repeat transactions.</p>
                <p>Launched as a series of experiments that saw a stat significant 0.5-2% increase in loan repayment rates; individual winners graduated to production.</p>
                <p><a href="https://www.figma.com/file/Z6ynTFkkTT6ulusqfagyLr/portfolio?type=design&node-id=993%3A2959&mode=design&t=QaAWrVt3ZoaAdzhD-1" class="button">View study</a></p>
