            <div class="description">
                <h1>Affirm</h1>
                <h2>2021 • Recommended Help Channels</h2>
                <q>I'm so frustrated trying to find answers to my question on the website, so I just Googled your customer support number.</q>
                <p>Customers miss opportunities for easy self service within the Affirm Help Center, so we introduced a contact flow that suggests channels for the best outcomes based on the customer's query.</p>
                <p>After launch there was a 31% increase in Affirm's CSAT score and a 32% decrease in support contacts.</p>
